Dear V.C. Andrews Fan:
 
All the DeBeers secrets are revealed at last...and you can know them even
before HIDDEN LEAVES hits the shelves!
 
That's right, the latest chapter in the gripping saga of Willow DeBeers
arrives as an eBook this week! And at SimonSaysShop.com, it's yours for just
$3.49 (that's 50% off the print book price!)
 
Who's Willow's real father? Why was her adoptive mother so cruel? And why
couldn't her birth mother keep her?  
 
Still reeling from the tragic death of her adoptive father, Willow comes
into possession of a family diary filled with all of the secrets her life --
and it changes her own life forever! HIDDEN LEAVES is the most stunning
chapter yet in this gripping saga.
 
Buy the eBook now!
http://www.simonsays.com/subs/book.cfm?areaid=358
<http://www.simonsays.com/subs/book.cfm?areaid=358&isbn=0743462653>
&isbn=0743462653
 
You might just want to pick up the print edition of HIDDEN LEAVES on 2/25 as
well -- it's the first time you'll see DARK SEED in print. The prequel to
the fantastic DeBeers family saga alongside the revealing new novel -- the
perfect combination!
 
Check out the print edition:
http://www.simonsays.com/subs/book.cfm?isbn=0743457870
<http://www.simonsays.com/subs/book.cfm?isbn=0743457870&areaid=11>
&areaid=11
 
*   *   *
And for everything V.C. Andrews, from familiar classics to future favorites,
visit www.simonsaysauthors.com/vcandrews
<http://www.simonsaysauthors.com/vcandrews> 
 
Good reading!
 
SimonSays.com
 

